name: SLICED LIVELY LEMON EARRINGS
description:
Suckin' on a Lemon Earrings!!!!

These weeny little babies are approx 4mm across, and are attached to clear plastic earring posts with rubber stoppers.

This kind of stud is excellent for allergy sufferers as they are completely non-metal.

Available in other designs too - including fried eggs, cucumber, kiwi fruit, tomatoes and oranges.

Thanks for looking!

www.foundlingsjewellery.co.uk
